title: Nominations Sent to the Senate 3/12/09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




March 12, 2009

 



Nominations Sent to the Senate 3/12/09




THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary  ____________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                    March 12, 2009    NOMINATIONS SENT TO THE SENATE:          Thomas L. Strickland, of Colorado, to be Assistant Secretary for   Fish and Wildlife, vice R. Lyle Laverty. Alexander Vershbow, of the District of Columbia, to be an   Assistant Secretary of Defense, vice Mary Beth Long, resigned.
